headline: General Electric (GE): Evaluating Current Valuation After Recent Steady Gains in Share Price
summary: If you’ve been keeping an eye on General Electric (GE) lately, the latest price action probably caught your attention. Shares climbed marginally higher to close at $266.44, but it isn’t a blockbuster move or the result of headline-grabbing news.
